{"tid":898360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸人又來借錢買麵包","createTime":"2018-11-11T15:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T06:23:36.000Z","uid":79668,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"879808af0ea58b1e02072108a441eb4a73d74bb9","tid":898360,"uid":79668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T15:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UfaxxD9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUfaxxD9.png&h=2ee95055&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n<br />\n大陸人: 不好意思，姐姐有些事，請問可以幫我一下嗎？<br />\n我: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大陸人: 就是，我姐妹在機場，我的卡@#/%...可以借點錢給我嗎？<br />\n我: 我得20蚊，m記加大都唔夠。<br />\n大陸人: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以買個麵包給我嗎？<br />\n我: 禾也要痴包呀，我把包皮給你<br />\n大陸人: 算了，沒關係<br />\n<br />\n之後我行去車站，又見到佢係度撩第二個，原來佢仲有個同黨，無啦啦行過來問我跟蹤佢地做乜<br />\n<br />\n大陸人: 你不覺得無聊嗎？<br />\n我: 我等車<br />\n大陸人: 我剛看見你拍照，你把圖片刪了<br />\n我死都話無，叫我開電話比佢睇<br />\n我: 你都on9 <br />\n<br />\n呢個時候，佢另外一個姐妹拎部電話出來，話叫人來喎<br />\n大陸人: 這裏有個小夥子拍了照，你們來幾個人吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後佢對住佢個姐妹講，內容大概係咩佢地應該係附近，應該幾分鐘就來到<br />\n<br />\n之後個女人對住我講: 香港人素質真差，要我不是我們大陸人來消費，你們香港人早就吃屎了<br />\n<br />\n我: 咁你問我借錢做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，屎都唔比你食呀，臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講完，巴士就到，佢問做咩唔繼續等<br />\n我: 再見啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  隱約聽到佢講吃屎吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上車之後，司機以為佢地想搭車，我同佢講返件事<br />\n司機叫我借比佢，然後揸返佢兩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大陸人真係好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fea9eb1209f812db9e3a278c3689005b4754991","tid":898360,"uid":102765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T15:39:48.000Z","msg":"支那臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670d4425f434a279f010afa691ab2dba03d92482","tid":898360,"uid":94452,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T15:48:17.000Z","msg":"司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 揸返佢兩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598b70c1c6e9bfb919f14824761619e56bd6cd6e","tid":898360,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T15:49:17.000Z","msg":"魚蛋妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43d66d3891c1da6f415d863dd32e765452b944b","tid":898360,"uid":51769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:00:33.000Z","msg":"司機大佬好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da840e0a7b3619621ffce5e93f0aa84864475512","tid":898360,"uid":79668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:01:21.000Z","msg":"大家唔好借錢比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f1d71a9344390038cfc568f564ea1349907d80","tid":898360,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTim